       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CLSRUN7.
      * CLOSURE-SLA PENALTY RUN, ENABLED AFTER PILOT RATIFICATION.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-CLOSURE-PENALTY-FLAG PIC X VALUE 'Y'.
           88  CLOSURE-PENALTY-ON VALUE 'Y'.
       01  WS-CLOSE-DAYS   PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-DELAY-DAYS   PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-PENALTY-AMT  PIC 9(9) VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CLOSE-DAYS
           IF CLOSURE-PENALTY-ON
              IF WS-CLOSE-DAYS > 7
                 COMPUTE WS-DELAY-DAYS = WS-CLOSE-DAYS - 7
                 COMPUTE WS-PENALTY-AMT = WS-DELAY-DAYS * 500
              END-IF
           END-IF
           DISPLAY 'PENALTY: ' WS-PENALTY-AMT
           STOP RUN.
